%section.product-header
  .container
    .product-header-cable
      %h1 Right Angle
      %p The retro style complements vintage instruments and amps. The right angle connector is really useful in many situations. It's great if you like leaning your guitar against your amp.
      %p 15' right angle 1/4" instrument cable
      %h1 $55
      %p= link_to "Buy Now", "#", class: "btn btn-primary"
    .product-header-cable
      %h1 Straight
      %p You can never have too many straight quarter inch cables, so why not use have some with style. We love this 50s-style connectors. They are study, easy to grip and hold up over heavy use.
      %p 15' straight 1/4" instrument cable
      %h1 $55
      %p= link_to "Buy Now", "#", class: "btn btn-primary"
    .product-header-cable
      %h1 XLR Microphone
      %p A multi-purpose cable for home recording and gigs. We made it long enough to stretch across the room from your drum overheads to the mixer, yet not too long for use at a small gig or rehearsal space.
      %p 25' XLR microphone cable
      %h1 $55
